data.description: OFFER DEADLINE SET FOR MONDAY, FEBRUARY 5 AT NOON.  Beautiful 3-level townhouse with open floor plan and lots of natural light.   The Grove at Huntley Meadows community backs up to Huntley Meadows Park.  Newly carpeted and painted throughout.  The kitchen features plenty of counter space and storage.  Newer HVAC and Water Heater.  Master suite features walk-in closet, large bathroom with dual vanities, stand-alone shower and soaking tub. Lower level has gas fireplace and storage space.  Conveniently located to Ft. Belvoir, Inova Mt. Vernon Hospital, Costco, the Beltway, and the Huntington Metro Station.
